[R1] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'O1VGQbYca5TEIHRgwhKZ_A', 'user_id': 'fLw53CbhJ1rue3iSga_m4g', 'business_id': '6a4gLLFSgr-Q6CZXDLzBGQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "I visited this place with 3 others for the first time.  The restaurant itself is really nice. The menu is compact and initially I wasn't sure I was going to like it. I ordered the Woodfire Oysters, the Oyster Sandwich and the pineapple upside down cake. The Woodfire Oysters were delicious. I just wish there were more of them for the price. The Oyster sandwich was HUGE but it was also delicious. The slaw paired with it was good too. However, I wasn't a fan of the Pineapple Upside Down cake. It tasted like it was made with cornbread or some sort of grainy bread... I also like that I was able to pay and tip really easily by scanning a code on my phone.  Overall though, it was a good experience. I'd go back.", 'date': '2021-08-15 14:14:33'}
[R2] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'T5OOIoqjWJGd4Dlv-r_MQA', 'user_id': 'SlVL5EffSFURh4pHZ7jm0Q', 'business_id': '6a4gLLFSgr-Q6CZXDLzBGQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Delicious food. The rabbit and dumplings was perfect. Filet was well seasoned and tasty. Boudin balls were delicious too. Nice pour on cocktails. We didn't try dessert.", 'date': '2021-08-15 14:40:07'}
