[R36] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '1gLeNpxK_c1kBb_zjPx4Ag', 'user_id': 'pHK725sGZlcYu8pdpPU_-Q', 'business_id': '6a4gLLFSgr-Q6CZXDLzBGQ', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Wonderful food, great service, chef is an awesome person too. We've been coming here for years, whenever we are in town. Often have my birthday dinner here with a large group. Never a disappointment, always a pleasure. Can't wait to return!", 'date': '2021-12-20 00:30:58'}
[R37] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'tgtKf_nZh1OLpGOW45-erQ', 'user_id': 'oqJAYJtqO2M6uvj1XQy6aQ', 'business_id': '6a4gLLFSgr-Q6CZXDLzBGQ', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Good, but not great. We enjoyed the dishes but nothing was a wow. Seemed to be coasting and not trying for fresh ideas and imaginative.', 'date': '2021-12-22 06:46:01'}
[R38] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'cvqFNdwfXR4IJKVqr6tZvQ', 'user_id': 'DysPZIk0Zs719tX5lBl22w', 'business_id': '6a4gLLFSgr-Q6CZXDLzBGQ', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Unfortunately Cochon has definitely gone downhill since we last ate here. For what you pay, the service is quite sloppy, and the food is somewhat lacking.

For example, our server forgot to review the beef/fish/pork options on the menu when she was taking our drink order; we didn't get bread until long after our appetizers arrived; we ordered a dessert wine with our dessert and were told they couldn't find it after we had already finished the food...

In terms of the main courses: the Cochon tasted good, but there was more fat than actual meat on the portion. My meal partners kept cutting and digging for an inordinate amount of time to actually find bits of meat to eat. We also ordered the gulf fish dish, and it was rather overcooked, the skin was unscaled (and therefore inedible), and it was strangely under-seasoned and flavorless.

