[R37] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'x9o-6lUanKzQfyRZasiUbA', 'user_id': '6Y5jT0xfYBmXWkBOqwDTjw', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 4.0, 'useful': 1, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The service was good but the waiter seemed like he was acting in a play with his way overdone Southern accent. The food seemed a little off.The duck breast was way too fatty. Maybe that is the way it is prepared but it was unlike any other restaurant where I have had duck. I had to separate the fat from the breast meat to eat it. The strudel was way overcooked. The Commander's champagne was good. I was curious why some tables got an amuse bouche and others didn't.", 'date': '2021-12-24 15:49:59'}
[R38] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'x8Jh0lR1Is6XhcR5pV9q5Q', 'user_id': 'voVeJcHVZLRZGrd7UAslHA', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 4, 'funny': 2, 'cool': 3, 'text': "It doesn't take long to see why Commander's Palace is a New Orleans institution.  The service was completely on point, everything ran like a well oiled machine, and some of the most sinfully delicious food you'll ever eat just gets cranked out like it's nothing - when one dish was done the next dish was already ready for us.  

I had the turtle soup, the smoked duck breast, and finished with the bread pudding souffle.  My wife had the gumbo, the shrimp and greens and also ended with the bread pudding souffle.  Simply put, everything they put in front of us was outrageously good.  Eating here was a top notch dining experience that was truly memorable.", 'date': '2021-12-27 04:32:42'}
[R39] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'WMFFJYCDPtf-sMxccyqlPg', 'user_id': 'tsCAjXT2oQn-cdGamwHQ9g', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 1, 'text': 'Commanders fully lives up to its reputation. Eating there is a full experience and it doesnt matter what meal you go for, you will have an amazing meal and a great time. Would 1000% ordering the bananas foster; they make it at your table and tell you the history of the dish. The whole place starts smelling like caramel and bananas and the taste is just as good as the smell! The gumbo and turtle soup are other must haves, along with the bread pudding!', 'date': '2021-12-27 05:32:48'}
[R40] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '9SIgm4W9KmrIQPcjpmBxAA', 'user_id': 'lAZP6KPG7Hr3cDFV6Cj_Lw', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'This is a second review of this restaurant, and I am a true believer in Commanders Palace now! First, nothing makes me happier as a Yelp elite reviewer than when a manager or owner comes over and greets the tables. On this particular night my party was greeted by the owner of the restaurant not once but twice as she made her way around to all of the tables in the dining room. This is a true showing of Class and Customer Service. In the midst of everything that she is responsible for as an owner she took the time to come by two times in the few hours that we were there to eat our meal that is a class act. Our waitress her name was Keisha and she was fantastic, very lovely and knowledgeable of the menu and she took really good care of us. The food was fantastic and the desserts were to die for. The matrody greeted us as if we were family returning home from a vacation which was also nice. But the evening began when we arrived and the valet outside was beyond nice and accommodating for my party. He was all smiles and I wish I knew his name because he definitely deserves recognition for having been at this location for years, I remember seeing him the last time I was in town. Service starts with the first person that we experience and for us it was the valet. Definitely recommend this restaurant and everyone who works there from the outside to the inside, enjoy!', 'date': '2022-01-02 01:35:33'}
[R41] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'G0wVKcLAQD2lfqUH34_d1Q', 'user_id': '6u49z3pjNVKs1O4rBmKXvA', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 2, 'funny': 1, 'cool': 2, 'text': "Amazing service, great food and drinks. 

