Of course, the main reason we came here was to try the turtle soup, as I'm sure many do, and we gave it a try; we actually really enjoyed it. There are shreds of meat instead of chunks, and it was sort of like gumbo consistency. Mild flavored broth and neither bland nor salty. Fun to try at least once. 

