[R7] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'rFdW_rYd4Ud7r4MZ5hv6Eg', 'user_id': 'nHE4uQoOwmQNstD2NddCkg', 'business_id': '_C7QiQQc47AOEv4PE3Kong', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "People rave of this place and give you nearly impossible expectations and it's about 99% on point. You expect servers that are clairvoyant and... no, but they are indeed great. They actually seem happy to be there, which makes the entire service more pleasant.

