[R1] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'toEAbQHYAURILaxlADYgbw', 'user_id': 'UzVUBcqL2Ht6v-KjLNRGgA', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 4, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 4, 'text': 'Three of us dined here on the 1st of January at about 7 PM.  We waited in line outside for about 15 minutes but the host did a great job managing the line and seating people as quickly as possible. The line was managed very actively and very professionally considering the chaos and obviously hammered patrons. We were seated outside in the center courtyard and were attended to very well by Zach, our server. Zach was very also a very helpful guide with info on NOLA!  Nice touch.

We ordered a number of items for the three of us to sample, the fried palter, the redfish, and the NOLA sampler.  They were all just ok.  Nothing of anything stood out as particularly note worth, certainly, nothing stood out as very "cajun" as it was all incredibly mild and had none of the note-worthy flavors of NOLA we were hoping to experience. It was hot, seemed fresh enough, and came quickly.  That's about it... It was not bad, but it definitely was not a standout experience either.  It was an ok experience and makes sense that it was so easy to get into versus some of the other establishments that had huge lines.  I think the length of the line tells the story of what you can expect.

Cheers to an epic 2022 and I hope NOLA bounces back well after the latest storm and COVID!', 'date': '2022-01-03 15:48:05'}
[R2] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '4p_tQeWQfVamd9HLoyVxtA', 'user_id': 'Y3opWVfXxR6AoG0RBHl0fA', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Food was good but the bartender on the third floor on New Year's Day was rude. I wanted to get an appetizer as my entree and she would not let me do that. I was told that I had to get a side if I wanted to get the gator bites as my main dish. Me and my girlfriend ordered the seafood pasta, a hurricane, spinach dip, and the gator bites and was told that was not enough and had to order a side with the gator bites. I don't like being told what to order.", 'date': '2022-01-03 18:36:44'}
