[R46] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '7YiO1jTqTgokw4-sgVuxpA', 'user_id': 's9p8Hx6ZKOlWv6VEVrQuVA', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "Ordered a cup of gumbo and the red beans and rice through DoorDash.  The delivery was fast.  The gumbo and the red beans and rice were very good but the $16 charged for the small quantity of red beans and rice was absolutely ridiculous. Food was 4-5 starts but due to price, I'm giving it 3 stars.  Looks like this place may be in the French Quarter, hence the high prices.  Do go, but hold on to your wallet.", 'date': '2022-01-18 02:05:03'}
[R47] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'e0ZMzh9LD3b3rxnUofojEQ', 'user_id': 'js_92iRSIp9gKGduy4kvoQ', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "If we could give half stars I'd give 2.5. The service was great and crab cakes were good and that's about it. I ordered the Louisiana platter. The gumbo was about 90% rice, the beans were about 60% rice, the jambalaya tasted stale like it was sitting there awhile. On top of that the bathroom was flooded and all dirty inside. Maybe it was a bad day but definitely my least favorite dinner spot during our visit.", 'date': '2022-01-19 01:32:58'}
[R48] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': 'gjmdCfZxygSGVWB8HiSh7A', 'user_id': 'LBQeqTxsjo84F8146DqnzQ', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "The best crab cakes I've ever had. I mean everything was delicious. We were recommended to try Oceana by the concierge of our hotel, straight off the plane and it was one of the best experiences of our trip. The staff was so warm and welcoming and our waiter, with the distinct deep Louisiana voice (who's name escapes me but it starts with an O) gave us the best menu recommendations and the best service. We will be going back on our next trip to NOLA! Crab Cakes and Chargrilled Oysters a must! Oh, and delicious Hurricane cocktail!", 'date': '2022-01-19 14:37:06'}
[R49] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '_LuPE2z0fUvxZ0pXfVhpSQ', 'user_id': 'TqIYJyMkFj-2gYpRbk-bwA', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 5.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': 'Our family was visiting from Florida and stopped in. We absolutely loved this place The staff was super friendly from the moment we walked in and all the way through our meal. Our server Corey was AMAZING!!! The food was delicious from start to finish... very impressed all around!! I highly recommend Oceania!!!', 'date': '2022-01-19 15:09:58'}
[R50] {'_type': 'review', 'review_id': '0s6ngEsSL8Eoqr5RckSTGw', 'user_id': 'FpfV9j0qTfNXfZtPhzfsbw', 'business_id': 'ac1AeYqs8Z4_e2X5M3if2A', 'stars': 3.0, 'useful': 0, 'funny': 0, 'cool': 0, 'text': "This was an okay bar. The food was not great but It was not horrible. We went twice. The first time we had dinner, which was a side of fettuccine and oysters. The oysters were fine but in all of Louisiana (okay in the French quarters) they don't serve vignette with oysters. Also, these warm
